data.description: Unveiling a delightful gem in the heart of Medford! Located on a quiet street, this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home boasts over 1100 sqft of sheer coziness. Step into the spacious living room and be embraced by the warm ambiance of a cozy gas fireplace with brick surround. The kitchen offers stainless steel appliances, a spacious eating area and an attached laundry room - enhancing functionality and convenience. Each bedroom is good size, providing plenty of space for family and guests! The expansive backyard is fully fenced and offers so much potential. Whether it's gardening, barbecues, or simply lounging under the open sky, this space is your canvas for outdoor enjoyment. The property also includes an attached 2-car garage and potential RV parking! Don't miss your chance to call this place home!
